1. It breaks apart a word into individual letters - bread - "b" "r" "e" "a" "d"
2. It looks for the same amount of letters in two arrays
                                                  - b r e a d - t a b l e
3. It looks for the same letters in two arrays - b r e a d - b e a r d
4. It puts together the letters that match the criteria - bread - beard
